   necessary to avoid thermal instability of the plasma edge. Stationary
   operation with type III ELMs imposes an upper limit on the edge
   temperature. Within the entire range of boundary densities investigated
   (n(e,b) less than or equal to 8 x 10(19) m(-3)), both L-mode and H-mode
